Package: cdmAcm0013
Title: Implementation of CDM Large-Scale Methodology ACM0013
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Christiaan", family = "Pauw", email = "christiaan.pauw@gmal.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Provides tidyverse-aligned tooling to operationalise the Clean Development Mechanism methodology ACM0013 "New grid-connected fossil fuel plants using a less greenhouse gas intensive technology". The package exposes applicability checks, equation-level helpers, monitoring-period aggregation, simulation utilities, and a meta-estimator that reproduces greenhouse gas accounting for efficient fossil-fuel power projects displacing more carbon intensive generation on the grid.
